29 format prescribed by the State Registrar.
30 (2) Certificates of death may not include a date of
31 disposition.
32 (b) Information required in certificates or reports
33 authorized by this chapter may be filed and registered by
34 photographic, electronic, or other means as prescribed by the
35 State Registrar."
36 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
37 1, 2026.
